title: Bug 116564: Incorrect title of hyperlink builder
OB: When I click on 'OK' and then reopen the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: Bug 116564: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it currently changes with the settings.
SR:
Steps to Reproduce: 
1. Open the hyperlink builder. 
2. Click on 'OK'. 
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder. 

Actual Behavior: The title of the hyperlink builder becomes 'www.actuate.com'. 
Expected Behavior: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
